name: Wilderness Sunset Interpretation
description:
After trekking 10 hours and over 44kms, my last drop of physical stamina was spent but my mind couldn’t allow this moment to quietly vanish from existence.  It willed my body into action to preserve this spectacular moment in time.  Looking back I am extremely happy it did.  The image is a perfect fit for an AI interpretive piece in which the original texture and feel are enhanced and transformed into a unique standalone piece.

Dimensions:3352 × 2388
